{"article_id":"swGghTrChKbVj9wN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"MCALLEN , Texas/WASHINGTON","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Flanked by border agents","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"who are going without paychecks during a government shutdown ,","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump threatened on Thursday to use emergency powers","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"to bypass Congress","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"to pay for a wall on the U.S.-Mexico border .","depth":12},{"id":7,"text":"Trump flew to the Texas border with Mexico","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"to try to bolster his case for the border wall","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"as a partial U.S. government shutdown","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"tied to the issue","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"stretched into its 20th day with no sign of new talks","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"to resolve the impasse .","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"\" We can declare a national emergency .","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"We shouldn ' t have to , \"","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"Trump told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"\" This is just common sense . \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Such a step would likely prompt an immediate legal challenge over constitutional powers from congressional Democrats","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"- a challenge","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"Trump said","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"he would win .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"The Republican president is adamant","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that a government funding bill","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"to end the shutdown","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"include $ 5.7 billion for a border barrier","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"- his signature campaign promise .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Congressional Democrats oppose that .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"The standoff has left a quarter of the federal government closed down and hundreds of thousands of federal employees without pay .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"A day after he stormed out of a meeting with Democratic leaders ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Trump attacked them","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"for refusing his demand ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"calling them harder to deal with than China , a rival power .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"\" I find China , frankly , in many ways to be far more honorable than Crying Chuck and Nancy .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"I really do , \"","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"referring to House of Representatives Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Senate Democratic leader Chuck Schumer .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"The House passed two bills","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to fund the departments of transportation , housing and agriculture","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"- each drawing a few more Republican votes than a similar effort on Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"to reopen the Treasury Department and other agencies .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"The White House has said","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Trump would veto the bills","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"if they made it to his desk .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Trump canceled plans","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to attend the World Economic Forum in Davos , Switzerland ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"which is scheduled to start on Jan. 22 ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"signaling","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"he was prepared for the shutdown to drag on .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"\" I have never been more depressed about moving forward than right now .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"I just don ' t see a pathway forward , \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"said Republican Senator Lindsey Graham , a Trump ally ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"who said","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"it was time for Trump to declare a national emergency .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"his lawyers had told him","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"he had the power","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"to invoke national emergency powers","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"to get his wall funded .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"\" I have the absolute right","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"to declare a national emergency , \"","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"Trump told reporters at the White House .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"\" I ' m not prepared to do that yet ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"but","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"if I have to ,","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"I will . \"","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"The declaration would circumvent Congress ' power over the national purse strings .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"A subsequent court fight could be protracted .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"The Washington Post ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"citing two unnamed sources ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"reported","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that the White House was laying the groundwork","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"for declaring an emergency","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that would let Trump build sections of a wall ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"possibly using funds from the Army Corps of Engineers .","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"NBC News , in a similar report , said","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Trump had been briefed on the plan","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"involving the Army Corps","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"while flying to the border on Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"A White House official denied","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Trump had been briefed on the plan ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"and the Pentagon declined to comment on the news reports .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"President Donald Trump salutes a U.S. Border Patrol helicopter with U.S. Border Patrol agents","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"as it flies over the Rio Grande River during his visit to the U.S. - Mexico border in Mission , Texas , U.S. , January 10 , 2019 .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"/Leah Millis","depth":5},{"id":84,"text":"Senator Joe Manchin , a moderate Democrat","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"who has cultivated good relations with Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"told reporters","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"a national emergency declaration by Trump would be \" wrong ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"but I think","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"that ' s his only way out \" of the impasse .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"If Trump were to make such a declaration ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"Manchin predicted","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"the Senate would immediately pass legislation","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"to fund the federal agencies","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that have been partially closed .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Pressure on both sides could intensify on Friday","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"when about 800,000 federal employees miss their first paychecks .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"About half of them are deemed \" essential \" to national security , like prison guards and airport security screeners -","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"and have to continue working .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Others are home on furlough .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"At the FBI ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"where most agents continue to work ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"concerns are building","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that operational funds","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"the bureau needs","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"to conduct investigations ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"including sensitive undercover operations ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"are beginning to dry up ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"said Tom O ' Connor , president of the FBI Agents Association .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"The shutdown ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"which began on Dec. 22 ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"will be the longest in U.S. history","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"if it is still going on by Saturday .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"In Texas , Trump focused on stories","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"told by tearful family members of people","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"killed by illegal immigrants ,","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"and was shown plastic-wrapped bricks of heroin , bales of marijuana , guns and a bag full of cash","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"seized by border agents .","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"Trump says","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"undocumented immigrants and illegal drugs are streaming across the border ,","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"despite statistics","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"that show","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"illegal immigration there is at a 20-year low","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"and that many drug shipments likely are smuggled through legal ports of entry .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Raul Ortiz , a local border patrol official , told Trump and reporters","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"that 133 people from countries other than Mexico and those in central America","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"- including India , Pakistan , China and Romania -","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"had been apprehended in the stretch of territory around McAllen .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"Just across the Rio Grande , in the Mexican city of Reynosa , a dozen recent deportees and U.S.-bound migrants gathered near a cross","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"that memorialized dead migrants .","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"Plagued by kidnappings ,","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"Reynosa is so dangerous for migrants","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"that locals advise new arrivals against any trip alone out of the two shelters .","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"\" Building a wall for a country , a nation so big , for a border so immense , so many kilometers is ridiculous , \"","depth":5},{"id":134,"text":"said Jose Ramon Poso Briseno , a Honduran man","depth":6},{"id":135,"text":"who has waited in a Reynosa shelter for five months","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"but has so far balked at crossing the river out of fear of cartel violence .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":0,"right":272,"rela